						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged and the date is partly lost. It mentions the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Virōdhi (= A.D. 1529-30)</hi> in the reign of <hi rend="bold">Achyutarāya-Mahārāya</hi> and records the gift made by him of the revenue raised in the bazaar street of <hi rend="bold">Vijaya-Virupāpura</hi> for the service of the god Mallikārjunadēva.</p>						

